{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-bookstore-page","demoType":"onLoad","title":"Korak 1","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj radionici, kreiraćete stranicu knjižare tako što ćete napraviti kartice knjiga koje prikazuju informacije o različitim knjigama. Naučićete kako da strukturirate sadržaj koristeći elemente <code>div</code>, klase, i ID-ove.</p>\n<p>Počnite sa vašom stranicom knjižare kreiranjem osnovnog dizajna HTML.</p>\n<p>Dodaj izjavu za <code>&#x3C;!DOCTYPE html></code> i komponente od <code>html</code> i <code>head</code>.</p>\n<p>Dodajte atribut <code>lang</code> elementu <code>html</code> i postavite ga na <code>\"en\"</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"69134b6cb43aa5f254950a10","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"basic-html","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-1"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[0,2],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da sadrži deklaraciju za <code>&#x3C;!DOCTYPE html></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<!DOCTYPE html>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da sadrži otvarajuće i zatvarajuće oznake za <code>&#x3C;html></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<html\\b[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*<\\/html>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaše svojstvo za <code>html</code> trebalo bi imati svojstvo elementa <code>lang</code>, postavljeno na <code>\"en\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<html[^>]*\\blang\\s*=\\s*[\"']en[\"'][^>]*>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da sadrži otvarajuće i zatvarajuće tagove za <code>&#x3C;head></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<head>[\\s\\S]*<\\/head>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Element vašeg <code>head</code> treba da bude smešten unutar elementa <code>html</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<\\/html>\\s*$/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/basic-html/#workshop-bookstore-page","dashedName":"step-1","certification":"basic-html","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"basic-html","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"workshop-bookstore-page","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-2","prevChallengePath":"/learn/basic-html/lecture-html-fundamentals/what-is-the-role-of-the-script-element-in-html","id":"69134b6cb43aa5f254950a10","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <title>XYZ Bookstore Page</title>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <h1>XYZ Bookstore</h1>\n  <p>Browse our collection of amazing books!</p>\n\n  <div class=\"card-container\">\n     <div class=\"card\" id=\"sally-adventure-book\">\n     <h2>Sally's SciFi Adventure</h2>\n     <p>\n          This is an epic story of Sally and her dog Rex as they navigate\n          through other worlds.\n     </p>\n     <button class=\"btn\">Buy Now</button>\n     </div>\n\n     <div class=\"card\" id=\"dave-cooking-book\">\n     <h2>Dave's Cooking Adventure</h2>\n     <p>\n          This is the story of Dave as he learns to cook everything from\n          pancakes to pasta, one recipe at a time.\n     </p>\n     <button class=\"btn\">Buy Now</button>\n     </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>Review your selections and continue to checkout.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"btn-container\">\n     <button id=\"view-cart-btn\" class=\"btn\">View Cart</button>\n     <button id=\"checkout-btn\" class=\"btn\">Checkout</button>\n  </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}